{"tid":423353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"邪惡！ 中國疑似製造「嬰兒肉膠囊」","createTime":"2017-10-03T23:55:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-05T13:46:18.000Z","uid":13468,"like":3,"dislike":77,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"6799344ac22dba1d6d913462f2d2344ed0d5f55b","tid":423353,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-03T23:55:26.000Z","msg":"邪惡！ 中國疑似製造「嬰兒肉膠囊」<br />\n<br />\n2017-10-03 15:59<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕南韓近3年來查獲8511粒「嬰兒肉膠囊」，多數是從中國走私進口。膠囊據稱是由流產或死胎嬰兒肉製成，食用者相信服用後對身體健康有益。<br />\n<br />\n據《韓國時報》報導，從2014年至今年6月為止，共有8511粒嬰兒肉膠囊被發現。自由韓國黨國會議員朴明在指出，過去大部分的的膠囊由國際包裹走私，但今年主要是旅客攜帶闖關，被嚴格的海關檢查發現。<br />\n<br />\n朴明在強調，必須要根除嬰兒肉膠囊的走私行為，並讓大眾認識到這是反人類罪行。朴明在說，認為嬰兒肉可以增進健康是誤解，這種膠囊其實對身體有害。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2212313\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2212313&d=A4g5XuAtNWp4SMA9AX0EISwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=f1411dea\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2212313&h=560cffa0\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2212313</a>"},{"pid":"18a2999be388408e53007e3884af9dc23821e230","tid":423353,"uid":139349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:03:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a143da63befeb4896ed52f5b15c1c5c331c48371","tid":423353,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:18:01.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"f0a87e1fcaedb8b64004da1d7c39c6ed1d877a73","tid":423353,"uid":40878,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:21:36.000Z","msg":"極邪惡 隱世 拉絲 强國人必食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0da02bca711e439cf74d43263a4682a4d54283","tid":423353,"uid":23874,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:26:10.000Z","msg":"紫河車<img src=\"/assets/faces/