e":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:34:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>紫河車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n紫河車唔係胎盤咩"},{"pid":"9e1db13dcf90d5e5e888bb52ef8d80d3ed697ac8","tid":423353,"uid":28240,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>究竟幾弱智嘅人先會信食左會有益健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n信奉支那文化的人</blockquote><br />\nbb時期吸收得好 <br />\n啲肉可能真係比一般肉多營養</blockquote><br />\n咪咁on9啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n即刻有人衝出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f79348e758253b5c02121a9f4f9e14db19f45af","tid":423353,"uid":13468,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:37:05.000Z","msg":"泡菜食人肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db970f87229bab7580882a52d98eb03c4728c4af","tid":423353,"uid":13468,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:39:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支那邊有真野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n先前就有韓國媒體深入調查發現，地下工廠從冰箱內取出胎兒屍體後，會先烘乾粉碎並加入中藥材，再裝進膠囊裡。一名參與「人肉膠囊」黑市交易的人士說，這些膠囊從延邊送到南韓後，透過中藥材業者送往市場，以「嬰兒膠囊」、「胎兒粉」的名稱對外銷售，100粒的銷售價格高達80萬韓元（約合台幣2萬元）。<br />\n<br />\n據南韓國立科學搜查研究院的化驗結果顯示，這種膠囊粉末中，化驗出的DNA和基因，與人類組織的相似度高達99.7%。而且在膠囊粉末中可以辨認出嬰兒毛髮和指甲等。南韓醫學界人士對此批評，除了沒有醫療效果外，如果病死胎兒或患有遺傳病，服用這種膠囊的人有可能感染意料不到的疾病。"},{"pid":"516b1a8b64c8a36ce9eebb9b263b4011fa9cdff2","tid":423353,"uid":38777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T00:48:12.000Z","msg":"支那人真係痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb30c62c72f064cb3704e0865728436ceb8ba46","tid":423353,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:06:16.000Z","msg":"CLS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938907693e79ad8d8b4d0bd0d6ce6dd55f48bd78","tid":423353,"uid":86701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:13:03.000Z","msg":"有病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a901a42ae61fd419b49d7808203c65ceb8ce5ee4","tid":423353,"uid":13495,"like":10,"dislike":10,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:23:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://att2.citysbs.com/hangzhou/2014/06/26/20/middle_426x600-201903_20731403785143120_7e2b069e98d22549f775645dfd1918c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fatt2.citysbs.com%2Fhangzhou%2F2014%2F06%2F26%2F20%2Fmiddle_426x600-201903_20731403785143120_7e2b069e98d22549f775645dfd1918c6.jpg&h=ccf8f932&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb7b92ea686e8d70fead2fa93543b09d3f315dcb","tid":423353,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:29:44.000Z","msg":"餃子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3d2e7bad1622603f33bbe46ebd73f9a82e11e7","tid":423353,"uid":50740,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:32:17.000Z","msg":"可能係假人肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4126469cdf09a436f25b48e8e31671c12b8ec02","tid":423353,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-04T01:34:27.000Z","msg":